Name: Courier Chief Tycoon
About the game: Welcome to Courier Chief Tycoon ! Courier Chief Tycoon is a game that lets you build and operate your own package delivery network. It offers you all the mechanics you need to grow your business. So what awaits you; -Couriers that you can assign in your company, -Different features from each other. -Panels where you can check your stock status, -Panels that you can order according to your needs. -Qualified software that you can purchase from your internet network, Each software has its own features. -The games on the site that you can use to add a new one to your entertainment, -Some games can earn you balance. -Crypto panels that you can navigate when you activate the secure network access, -You can provide additional income to your company and accelerate your development. -Engine gallery where you can give your employees an advantage with different engines, -Interactions where you can strengthen the engines you have. -Notification panels where you can check your customers' comments, -Control panels where you can deal with your customers' orders.
